{"id": 243378730, "title": "Air Fare Reduced: 20% discount on Akasa Airlines fare, this is how you can avail the offer", "text": "Air Travel Fare Reduced: If you are planning to travel by air, then there is a big offer going on in Akasa Airlines flights. Under this, you will get huge discounts on fares. Let\u2019s know how you can take advantage of this offer? Akasa Airlines Offers: Akasa Air, owned by the late Rakesh Jhunjhunwala, has launched a \u2018PAYDAY\u2019 sale to offer discounts on domestic flights. This sale will run from today till Monday. Meanwhile, passengers will get huge discounts on Akasa Air flights. Let us know how you can take advantage of this discount. Take advantage of the discount like this Under the \u2018PAYDAY\u2019 sale, Akasa Air is giving up to 20 percent discount to passengers on domestic flights. This discount will be available only on \u2018Saver\u2019 and \u2018Flexi\u2019 fares. For this, you will have to use the promo code \u2018PAYDAY\u2019 during booking. For this, air travel has to be booked through Akasa Air\u2019s website www.akasaair.com, mobile app or travel agent. Our Pay Day Sale is here. Time for a vacay! Get up to 20% off on flights. Use code: PAYDAY Offer valid till 1 July only. Hurry; book now: https://t.co/IUwGXBjFam#AkasaAir #ItsYourSky #PayDaySale pic.twitter.com/I4LUHa0bb8\u2014 Akasa Air (@AkasaAir) June 28, 2024 Sale will run from 28 June to 1 July Akasa Airlines said that passengers can avail this offer from 28 June to 1 July. This discount will be available on all 22 destinations on the airline\u2019s domestic network. He further said that booking has to be done seven days in advance for travel between 5 July and 30 September. This benefit can be availed on both one-way and round-trip tickets. These facilities will also be available in the planes Akasa Air said that their Boeing 737 Max aircraft have ample leg room and USB ports for charging devices for a comfortable and efficient flight. The airline\u2019s me